references in this discussion to total
corporate earnings mean net income attributable to exxonmobil (u.s. gaap) from
the consolidated income statement. unless otherwise indicated, references to
earnings, upstream, downstream, chemical and corporate and financing segment
earnings, and earnings per share are exxonmobils share after excluding amounts
